{"tid":2437963,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"裝修工及學生被控涉藏索帶白電油等物品 所有罪名不成立","createTime":"2021-03-08T07:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T12:06:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":42,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"74dbe94f6d94bead6004b8b5f7208eaf66d60cd4","tid":2437963,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:52:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14224\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14224&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058uQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=4b4ce9b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14224</a><br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第七庭<br />\n#葉啓亮裁判官<br />\n#1201尖沙咀 #裁決<br />\n#管有物品意圖損壞財產罪<br />\n#管有工具作非法用途<br />\n<br />\nD1:林(22)<br />\nD2:黃(23)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1)管有物品意圖摧毀或損壞財產 [D1]<br />\n（１支噴漆）<br />\n(2)管有適合作非法用途的工具 [D2]<br />\n （１包索帶）<br />\n(3)管有物品意圖摧毀或損壞財產 [D2]<br />\n（２罐白電油與１個打火機）<br />\n<br />\n承認事實 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12902\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12902&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058uQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=c0c6adbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12902</a>)<br />\nPW1 DPU10231鄧保麟 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12917\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12917&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058uQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=9b5c2dd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12917</a>)（追截D1）<br />\nPW2警員25070周天威 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12931\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12931&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058uQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=dd7df69d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12931</a>)（拘捕D1）<br />\nPW3警員17043佘裕城 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12950&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058uQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=fc61812a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12950</a>)（追截D2）<br />\nPW4警員24345 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12955\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12955&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058uQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=23ca18b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12955</a>)（拘捕D2）<br />\nD1及DW1 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12963\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12963&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058uQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=e1dada0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12963</a>)<br />\nD2及DW2 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13134\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13134&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058uQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=8c5810d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13134</a>)（待補完）<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n速報：🎊所有罪名不成立🎊<br />\n（詳情後補）"},{"pid":"a74b06c91b2153610ae4b60ced030ed7d466d886","tid":2437963,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1f684dd1a8079f5914e943c3060f2730ffa308","tid":2437963,"uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:53:25.000Z","msg":"拘捕首被告的警員承認見不到被告有任何破壞行為，但指現場有不少塗鴉。<br />\n<br />\n警員鄧保麟指，當日下午4時許有人在梳士巴利花園進行反修例示威，警方到場並舉藍旗警告，未幾有速龍小隊作出追捕，鄧見狀亦上前協助，並成功制服穿黑衣、孭着背囊及戴手套的被告。鄧承認沒有看見被告曾做過甚麼，但第一眼見到被告時，他身旁有不同反修例口號的塗鴉。<br />\n<br />\n警員周天威則指，當日執勤期間見到有同僚正制服首被告，為免有人搶犯或疑犯逃走，於是出手協助，並將被告帶往警署。他在警署搜被告的背囊時，搜出涉案噴漆，以及生理鹽水、黑色口罩和帽等。"},{"pid":"0a97b43d0c4bae4e30d52c6299cff767d403178b","tid":2437963,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:54:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14bbd7e7b4d5b41767358cce3fe1e011333a2cbd","tid":2437963,"uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:54:17.000Z","msg":"葉生一時時"},{"pid":"6ce57d7e2f91474aab7baa242e202d45deebbf1c","tid":2437963,"uid":271497,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:54:24.000Z","msg":"太好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"960383e48dae720c2b6dd4bf76c24bb330b817ed","tid":2437963,"uid":2054,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:55:53.000Z","msg":"去旅行啦<br />\n律政屍實上訴<br />\n上訴庭官比中共控制曬"},{"pid":"7559441397fb7e40dacd2c324e8b3a1d4a8f1ba9","tid":2437963,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T08:00:27.000Z","msg":"合理"},{"pid":"9332fa6a8db661a92b750dec62d6a64538c6225b","tid":2437963,"uid":306614,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T08:01:27.000Z","msg":"旅行 gogogo<br />\n拎住啲判詞同錢 仲有護照同其他行李 走得<br />\n去到扮旅客入境，跟住搵律師申請政治庇護<br />\n搵律師要錢 所以要帶一堆現金"},{"pid":"4e31c7dc56b9e9f139dfc818c6bd17c8eb20003a","tid":2437963,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T08:21:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b987cfeaf4a599351954796e9078703ea33a7f04","tid":2437963,"uid":358691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T08:26:33.000Z","msg":"去旅行呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ca92b4b74988d9a8e9c62504e2145dc51a674e","tid":2437963,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T08:29:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d526522b0fbbd3c9c601d3f870ad82ea2e23967e","tid":2437963,"uid":80393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T08:31:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a25b982ade6222abd7fd2b7308c05632eaa6cd","tid":2437963,"uid":3860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T08:31:47.000Z","msg":"即晚走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4cda3fba9c64147ef61355706f1418196cea5f","tid":2437963,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"960383e48dae720c2b6dd4bf76c24bb330b817ed","tid":2437963,"uid":2054,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:55:53.000Z","msg":"去旅行啦<br />\n律政屍實上訴<br />\n上訴庭官比中共控制曬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T08:32:35.000Z","msg":"真呀"},{"pid":"454c952589d9f7b77c0572a404553cf54a7cf774","tid":2437963,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:10:10.000Z","msg":"前年12月1日尖沙咀「毋忘初心大遊行」中，兩名男子涉嫌被搜出噴漆、白電油及索帶等物品，被控管有物品意圖摧毀或損壞財產、管有適合作非法用途的工具及管有物品意圖摧毀或損壞財物3罪。兩名被告今於九龍城裁判法院被裁定罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官葉啓亮表示，拘捕首被告的鄧警員證供混亂，曾推翻自己作供。鄧曾指被告先自行跑走，後來又改稱速龍小隊舉起藍旗向前推進後，被告才跑走。葉官認為警員證供於一些重要情節上未必可靠。另外，鄧警員亦曾表示首被告被捕時戴有手套，但另一名在場的周警員，卻指被告沒有手套，卻不知道為何拍照時變成有手套，葉官認為手套可協助判斷被告是否有不當意圖。<br />\n<br />\n另外，根據證人描述，次被告當時身穿紅衣，亦只在原地站立張望，明顯與其他「核心示威者」不同，而索帶一直放在背囊內，非觸手可及，索帶亦可以是日常用品。基於疑點利益歸於被告前提下，裁定兩名被告罪名不成立。"},{"pid":"a3cf103869cfde9a31df0c167d9a3795303e573e","tid":2437963,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"454c952589d9f7b77c0572a404553cf54a7cf774","tid":2437963,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:10:10.000Z","msg":"前年12月1日尖沙咀「毋忘初心大遊行」中，兩名男子涉嫌被搜出噴漆、白電油及索帶等物品，被控管有物品意圖摧毀或損壞財產、管有適合作非法用途的工具及管有物品意圖摧毀或損壞財物3罪。兩名被告今於九龍城裁判法院被裁定罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官葉啓亮表示，拘捕首被告的鄧警員證供混亂，曾推翻自己作供。鄧曾指被告先自行跑走，後來又改稱速龍小隊舉起藍旗向前推進後，被告才跑走。葉官認為警員證供於一些重要情節上未必可靠。另外，鄧警員亦曾表示首被告被捕時戴有手套，但另一名在場的周警員，卻指被告沒有手套，卻不知道為何拍照時變成有手套，葉官認為手套可協助判斷被告是否有不當意圖。<br />\n<br />\n另外，根據證人描述，次被告當時身穿紅衣，亦只在原地站立張望，明顯與其他「核心示威者」不同，而索帶一直放在背囊內，非觸手可及，索帶亦可以是日常用品。基於疑點利益歸於被告前提下，裁定兩名被告罪名不成立。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:30:32.000Z","msg":"單新聞出得幾快"},{"pid":"241a390b289078c7060ebcf534b403fc5839baa8","tid":2437963,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:39:03.000Z","msg":"恭喜手足"},{"pid":"1d81475e33cae70b279f76617833133ef71d0dde","tid":2437963,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T10:16:07.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴波衫手足個單?<br />\n<br />\n裁判官葉啓亮在裁決時表示，<span class=\"red\">負責制服首被告的警員鄧保麟，作供時一度推翻自己的說法</span>，原稱是被告先跑，警員才追截，後則稱是警員追截後被告才跑，認為警員在如此重要的追截過程亦有記憶混亂，其證供即使可信亦不一定可靠，無法協助法庭。另外，兩名作供警亦對被告當時有沒有戴手套有不同說法，而是否有戴上手套可協助判斷被告是否有不當意圖。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/12-1-%E5%B0%96%E6%B2%99%E5%92%80-%E5%85%A9%E7%94%B7%E8%97%8F%E5%99%B4%E6%BC%86%E7%B4%A2%E5%B8%B6-%E7%8D%B2%E5%88%A4%E7%84%A1%E7%BD%AA-%E5%AE%98-%E4%BD%9C%E4%BE%9B%E8%AD%A6%E8%A8%98%E6%86%B6%E6%B7%B7%E4%BA%82-%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E5%8F%AF%E9%9D%A0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F12-1-%25E5%25B0%2596%25E6%25B2%2599%25E5%2592%2580-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%2597%258F%25E5%2599%25B4%25E6%25BC%2586%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%25B8%25B6-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%2588%25A4%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E4%25BD%259C%25E4%25BE%259B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25A8%2598%25E6%2586%25B6%25E6%25B7%25B7%25E4%25BA%2582-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%258F%25AF%25E9%259D%25A0%2F&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058uQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=a148cd7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F12-1-%25E5%25B0%2596%25E6%25B2%2599%25E5%2592%2580-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%2597%258F%25E5%2599%25B4%25E6%25BC%2586%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%25B8%25B6-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%2588%25A4%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E4%25BD%259C%25E4%25BE%259B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25A8%2598%25E6%2586%25B6%25E6%25B7%25B7%25E4%25BA%2582-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%258F%25AF%25E9%259D%25A0%2F&h=88b1252f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/12-1-%E5%B0%96%E6%B2%99%E5%92%80-%E5%85%A9%E7%94%B7%E8%97%8F%E5%99%B4%E6%BC%86%E7%B4%A2%E5%B8%B6-%E7%8D%B2%E5%88%A4%E7%84%A1%E7%BD%AA-%E5%AE%98-%E4%BD%9C%E4%BE%9B%E8%AD%A6%E8%A8%98%E6%86%B6%E6%B7%B7%E4%BA%82-%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E5%8F%AF%E9%9D%A0/</a>"},{"pid":"ebb9dbd9d491979139993e2b549191c533251200","tid":2437963,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:01:38.000Z","msg":"葉官又指，兩名警員的證供有出入，追截林的警員曾供稱林帶有手套，惟拘捕警員則從未見林帶手套。葉官認為雖手套在案件中屬枝節，但為重要觀察，亦是考慮被告有否不合法意圖的因素。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210308/HFCBTDGXZFDRPEA4B3HYXJVYGM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210308%2FHFCBTDGXZFDRPEA4B3HYXJVYGM%2F&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058uQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=ce79176c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210308%2FHFCBTDGXZFDRPEA4B3HYXJVYGM%2F&h=25cb8bde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210308/HFCBTDGXZFDRPEA4B3HYXJVYGM/</a>"},{"pid":"2ff6d9ca1254c1d54288468fcbe9bb92ad42577f","tid":2437963,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c